title: Trans-Siberian Orchestra - Live With Kelly and Michael 2013 HDTV
description:
Trans-Siberian Orchestra
"Dreams of Fireflies" (On a Christmas Night)
December 24th, 2013
Live With Kelly and Michael

This video was captured directly from a digital cable box's HDMI output to MPEG4 in 1080i using a Game Capture HD and an HDMI splitter to remove HDCP.  

Since it was captured from cable, it is interlaced, and no re-encoding has been performed.  If you are playing back on a computer, please enable de-interlacing on your media player.  See below for complete technical specs on the video.
